    <div align="left" id="post_message_299705">Here is conversation with Psikotick I had about the campaign.  I edited out a lot of stuff to make it easier to read.<br />
 <br />
[13:52] aTchOfGrey: anywho, i started running that campaign and its going pretty well<br />
[13:52] aTchOfGrey: the basic premise is the Prophecy + Dogma + the cell, the plot is<br />
<br />
[13:52] aTchOfGrey: is that the angel gabriel(played by Christopher Walken a la Prophecy) has started a war in heavem for the favor of god<br />
[13:52] aTchOfGrey: he wants to kill all of mankind<br />
<br />
[13:52] aTchOfGrey: but<br />
[13:52] aTchOfGrey: angels were not created to be creative<br />
[13:53] aTchOfGrey: there is a stalemate and neither side can gain the tactical advantage<br />
<br />
<br />
[13:53] aTchOfGrey: and due to the war no souls are entering heaven<br />
[13:53] aTchOfGrey: gabriel has decided that his best bet<br />
<br />
[13:54] aTchOfGrey: is to find the soul of the most devious person alive<br />
[13:54] aTchOfGrey: tactician/strategist that is<br />
<br />
[13:54] aTchOfGrey: and kidnap them into helping his cause<br />
[13:54] aTchOfGrey: however<br />
[13:54] aTchOfGrey: the devil doesnt want gabriel to succeed<br />
[13:54] aTchOfGrey: well lucifer that is<br />
<br />
[13:55] aTchOfGrey: because if he does he's not gonna have people anymore to pick on<br />
<br />
[13:55] aTchOfGrey: so lucifer has been going out and kill all of the horrible people<br />
[13:55] aTchOfGrey: throughout time<br />
<br />
[13:55] aTchOfGrey: and trapping them in their own private hells<br />
[13:55] aTchOfGrey: so gabriel cant get them<br />
<br />
[13:56] aTchOfGrey: for many years there was a stalemate<br />
[13:56] aTchOfGrey: betwenn lucifer and gabriel and grabriel and the good angels<br />
[13:56] aTchOfGrey: the good angels are led by michael<br />
<br />
[13:56] aTchOfGrey: recently though<br />
[13:57] aTchOfGrey: Gabriel has brokered a deal with Azreal from Dogma<br />
[13:57] aTchOfGrey: (Jason Lee)<br />
[13:57] aTchOfGrey: You see Gabriel has just learned to lie<br />
[13:57] aTchOfGrey: and he has lied to azreal and said his plan is to destroy all of existance<br />
[13:58] aTchOfGrey: you see, Azreal believes that god can be defeated<br />
[13:59] aTchOfGrey: and that Gabriel can do it<br />
<br />
[13:59] aTchOfGrey: she/he<br />
[13:59] aTchOfGrey: its not quite the dogma universe<br />
[13:59] aTchOfGrey: view askew univers that is<br />
<br />
[13:59] aTchOfGrey: and gabriel has convinced azreal that once the humans are gone<br />
[14:00] aTchOfGrey: they can remake the world in their image<br />
[14:00] aTchOfGrey: meanwhile, the devil has his own agenda<br />
[14:00] aTchOfGrey: he take the guise of &quot;the angel of celestial light&quot;<br />
[14:01] aTchOfGrey: and is appearing to the player<br />
[14:01] aTchOfGrey: who is in actuallity &quot;THE LAST SCION!&quot;<br />
[14:01] TicKisMiKe: nice<br />
[14:01] TicKisMiKe: well, he IS the angel of light<br />
[14:01] aTchOfGrey: yah<br />
[14:01] TicKisMiKe: lucifer was one of 3 archangels<br />
[14:01] aTchOfGrey: so he's not even really lying<br />
[14:01] TicKisMiKe: right<br />
[14:01] aTchOfGrey: and he has convinced the player<br />
[14:01] aTchOfGrey: that the war in heaven<br />
[14:02] aTchOfGrey: has closed the gates of hell as well<br />
<br />
[14:02] aTchOfGrey: and as such angels can contact the lost souls who are destined to enter it<br />
[14:02] aTchOfGrey: the player's job is to enter their personal hells<br />
[14:02] aTchOfGrey: and save them<br />
[14:02] aTchOfGrey: by finding their soul<br />
[14:03] aTchOfGrey: which is usally represented by a blocvk of gold a la Pulp Fiction and ancient hindu myth<br />
<br />
[14:03] aTchOfGrey: usually though<br />
[14:03] aTchOfGrey: the soul is guarded by some great beast held in by the person's subconscious<br />
[14:03] aTchOfGrey: for example<br />
[14:04] aTchOfGrey: Billy the Kid's soul was held by a Sheriff McGarrett<br />
[14:04] aTchOfGrey: the man Billy couldnt gun down<br />
<br />
[14:04] aTchOfGrey: Al capone's soul was held by the warden and his demon dogs<br />
<br />
[14:05] aTchOfGrey: Albert Einstein's was held by himseld<br />
[14:05] aTchOfGrey: himself<br />
[14:05] aTchOfGrey: the player just had to convince him to get past the A-bomb<br />
<br />
[14:05] aTchOfGrey: and let him know that he owuld have a chance to make up for it<br />
<br />
[14:06] aTchOfGrey: that sucks, it was good<br />
[14:06] aTchOfGrey: However<br />
[14:06] TicKisMiKe: yeah, prolly gonna run it again online<br />
[14:06] aTchOfGrey: there are two characters that are actually working for the devil<br />
[14:06] aTchOfGrey: Vlad the Impaler<br />
[14:06] aTchOfGrey: and Hitler<br />
[14:07] aTchOfGrey: They've made a deal<br />
